"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f4ac6a44bc288f0f716ca5c4b6d7eacfdb5a10db","tid":2114134,"uid":165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"有,仲結埋婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"吓 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你有咩感受？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:08:31.000Z","msg":"我之後先知嘅，仲要奉子成婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢哋一齊嘅時候條女已經係背後中傷我<br />\n話我搵返佢傾偈<br />\n其實當時我已經有女朋友<br />\n咁我就好憎呢個女人嘅<br />\n我就同佢講麻煩你尊重下你男朋友<br />\n點知佢同條仔講話係我撩佢傾偈<br />\n咁條仔又以為我想撬佢牆腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同晒當時圈子嘅人講我勾二嫂<br />\n所以成班就同我絕交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真條女同我分手之後都唔知同過幾多人一齊喇<br />\n我又使唔使隔咗咁耐時間先至去搵佢傾偈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw我中學拍過四次拖，條友就同過我兩個ex一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔撚知係咪咁撚鍾意食二手飯<br />\n其中有一年佢仲要同我一齊坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197c9f4b8be0ed0df3d159bba2c6acc64147e2c9","tid":2114134,"uid":336070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eec859f865727ffed8f6a910ccc1acdc2bfb888b","tid":2114134,"uid":58333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"474f9ecbceec5054aba12295a184a4beb984f7e5","tid":2114134,"uid":336070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy